    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "へ～、愛ちゃんと千紗ちゃんが～\n割と仲がいいんですねぇ",
      "startTime": 4.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……さくらもこころも、今のところ動きがないわね\n絶対何か隠してると思うんだけど……",
      "startTime": 12.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、琴乃ちゃんだ\nどうかしたの？",
      "startTime": 19.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　あ……べ、別に……",
      "startTime": 20.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3866.6666666999986,
          "startTime": 24.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "別に……って感じではなかったですけどねぇ\n最近こころ達を探るような目で見てるじゃないですかー",
      "startTime": 30.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "さ、探ってなんか……あっ、そうだ！　ほら、こころに\n何がほしいのか聞いてなかったなって思って",
      "startTime": 39.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "企画のプレゼント、こころ達にもあげるつもりだから",
      "startTime": 43.1333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "怪しい……",
      "startTime": 47.1999987285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "なんで私の方が怪しまれてるの……！？\nと、とにかく、何がほしいか聞きたいのは本当――",
      "startTime": 52.9999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "わ……\nわーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーー！！",
      "startTime": 58.9666659037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ！？　び、びっくりした！\nいきなり何……！？",
      "startTime": 66.0999982198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃん、大変だよ！\n当日の天気予報が……！！",
      "startTime": 70.5333315532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "天気予報……？\n晴れーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーーー！？",
      "startTime": 76.0666648865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "えらいこっちゃ！　えらいこっちゃ！\nえらいこっちゃですよーーーー！！",
      "startTime": 79.7666648865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "よ、よく分からないんだけど、とりあえず\nこころのほしいものを教えてほしいんだけど……",
      "startTime": 87.0333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "それどころじゃないんですよ！\nえらいこっちゃなんですよ、琴乃ちゃん！",
      "startTime": 91.9999966939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ！　このままじゃ、琴乃ちゃんへの……\n琴乃ちゃんへの……っ……！",
      "startTime": 101.3666603088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃーーーーん！！",
      "startTime": 105.6999936421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "だからなんなのー！？",
      "startTime": 108.4999921162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "今更変える訳にもいきませんし、あわわ……！\nさくらちゃん、緊急作戦会議です！",
      "startTime": 114.7999956767,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8626.674550400012,
          "startTime": 123.4266702271
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、プレゼントはテキトーにかき氷機にでもしておいて\n下さい。夏にイタズラに使うので～。ではでは",
      "startTime": 120.83332901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "本当に、なんなんだろう……",
      "startTime": 126.9666587829,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6233.34325159999,
          "startTime": 133.2000020345
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――誕生日当日",
      "startTime": 131.7333254496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "こころー？　さくらー？　そろそろ準備しないと……\n……あれ？　庭の方から声が……",
      "startTime": 140.6999972026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "garden-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "雪よーーーーーーーーーーーー！！",
      "startTime": 146.5333356221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "降りたまへーーーーーーーーー！！",
      "startTime": 149.8666689555,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "お頼みもうすー！　お頼みもうすー！\nほんにゃらほんにゃらズンドコズンドコ！！",
      "startTime": 158.8666689555,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3966.6643778000152,
          "startTime": 162.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "……な……何、してるの？\nスタッフさん達まで巻き込んで……",
      "startTime": 169.0999982198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "見て分からないんですか！\n雨乞いならぬ、雪乞いですよっ！",
      "startTime": 173.900446701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "もう時間がないの！　ほら、琴乃ちゃんも！\nほんにゃらほんにゃらズンドコズンドコ！！",
      "startTime": 180.533342743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "ほ……ほんにゃらほんにゃらズンドコズンドコ……",
      "startTime": 184.833342743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "……って、こんなことしてる場合じゃないから！\nパーティーが始まっちゃう、スタッフさん達も隠れて！",
      "startTime": 194.1000012716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……こころちゃん、時間切れみたいだね……\nなんとかなれば良かったんだけど……",
      "startTime": 204.733334605,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
